    schema:description """With this subject, we intend to cover the mathematical foundations of Digital Signal Processing. The mathematical tools thus presented can also be applied in other fields, such as Systems Control and Image Processing. Matlab shall be the software used in the learning and evaluation activities.
Classes will be in English."""@es ;
